    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In mosques, high podiums on columns from which the celebrant's assistant repeats his Koran readings and gestures for the more distant worshippers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
